rows.label: bf09210100_0010
rows.name: Boy!

rows.label: bf09210100_0020
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: bf09210100_0030
rows.name: Do you like this world?

rows.label: bf09210100_0040
rows.name: What's with that question out of nowhere?

rows.label: bf09210100_0050
rows.name: Give me an honest answer.

rows.label: bf09210100_0060
rows.name: Yeah, I do.

rows.label: bf09210100_0070
rows.name: There are many things to worry about but

rows.label: bf09210100_0080
rows.name: there are even more wonderful things too.

rows.label: bf09210100_0090
rows.name: What about us?

rows.label: bf09210100_0100
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: bf09210100_0110
rows.name: Oh? Is this an unexpected love confession?

rows.label: bf09210100_0120
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Wha-?

rows.label: bf09210100_0130
rows.name:
You fool.
I was asking if you like humans.

rows.label: bf09210100_0140
rows.name: Oh, that scared me for a second.

rows.label: bf09210100_0150
rows.name: Why are you getting so flustered?

rows.label: bf09210100_0160
rows.name: So? What's your answer?

rows.label: bf09210100_0170
rows.name: That's a tough one.

rows.label: bf09210100_0180
rows.name:
"People can be fun to be around,
but sometimes they're hard to deal with.

rows.label: bf09210100_0190
rows.name:
And there are detestable types 
like Chairman Bahn too.

rows.label: bf09210100_0200
rows.name: You're right about that.

rows.label: bf09210100_0210
rows.name: But...

rows.label: bf09210100_0220
rows.name:
If all of that is part of what we call life, 
then yeah, I like it.

rows.label: bf09210100_0230
rows.name:
After all, if I didn't, 
I wouldn't be standing here now, would I?

rows.label: bf09210100_0240
rows.name: You're way too full of yourself.

rows.label: bf09210100_0250
rows.name:
Hahaha, I see
That's so like you, boy. That's a relief.

rows.label: bf09210100_0260
rows.name: What?

rows.label: bf09210100_0270
rows.name: Well...

rows.label: bf09210100_0280
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]?

rows.label: bf09210100_0290
rows.name:
What if someone who hates himself obtained power?
What do you think they would do?

rows.label: bf09210100_0300
rows.name: If someone like that were to meet God...

rows.label: bf09210100_0310
rows.name:
Wouldn't they just wish for 
the world to disappear... Don't you think...
